---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="For Buyers — Ayris Global"
  description="Ayris Global partners with wellness brands, supplement manufacturers, and ingredient buyers across the EU, UK, USA, UAE/GCC, Japan, Korea, ANZ, Southeast Asia, and Latin America. Discover why global buyers source Indian botanicals through Ayris Global."
>

  <!-- HowTo JSON-LD Schema (Session 28) -->
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={`{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"HowTo","name":"From Enquiry to Delivered Ingredient","description":"How global wellness ingredient buyers source Indian botanicals through Ayris Global, from initial enquiry to shipment.","step":[{"@type":"HowToStep","position":1,"name":"Submit Your Enquiry","text":"Tell us what you need: ingredient, form, specification, certifications required, quantity, and target market. Use the contact form or reach Ayris Global directly via email or WhatsApp."},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":2,"name":"We Match and Confirm","text":"Within 48 hours, Ayris Global confirms availability, matched producer capability, and provides an initial specification sheet and indicative pricing."},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":3,"name":"Sample Dispatch","text":"Samples are dispatched with full technical documentation, including Certificate of Analysis, Material Safety Data Sheet, and certification documents relevant to the buyer's market."},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":4,"name":"Order and Shipment","text":"On approval, Ayris Global manages the full order process: producer coordination, quality inspection, export documentation, and shipment, with one point of contact throughout."}]}`} slot="head" />

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════
       PAGE HERO
  ════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero__inner">
      <span class="eyebrow">For Global Buyers</span>
      <h1 class="page-hero__title">Why the World's Wellness Brands Source Through Ayris Global</h1>
      <p class="page-hero__sub">India produces more certified botanical ingredients than any other country on earth. Getting to the right producers — with the right certifications, the right documentation, and the right pricing — requires a partner who knows the supply chain from the ground up. That's what Ayris Global exists to do.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════
       ORIGIN SECTION
  ════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="origin">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="origin__inner">
        <div class="origin__text">
          <span class="section-eyebrow">Why India</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">The World's Most Important Botanical Origin</h2>
          <p>India holds a unique position in the global wellness ingredient economy. With the world's largest certified organic farming area, a 5,000-year tradition of botanical knowledge, and an unmatched diversity of growing climates — from the Himalayan foothills to the Kerala coast — no other origin offers the same breadth, depth, and certification infrastructure.</p>
          <p>Indian botanical producers now hold GMP, ISO, FSSAI, NPOP, NOP, Halal, and Kosher certifications at scale — meeting the compliance requirements of every major regulated market. The challenge for global buyers is not whether the ingredient exists. It's finding the right producer, at the right specification, at a price that works.</p>
          <p>Ayris Global exists to solve exactly that problem.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="origin__stats">
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat__num">5,000+</span>
            <span class="stat__label">Years of documented botanical practice</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat__num">#1</span>
            <span class="stat__label">Global producer of certified organic spices</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat__num">1,178</span>
            <span class="stat__label">Medicinal plant species in active trade (NMPB)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat__num">9</span>
            <span class="stat__label">Global markets we actively serve</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════
       WHAT WE OFFER BUYERS
  ════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="offer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-eyebrow">The Ayris Difference</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">What We Bring to Every Sourcing Partnership</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">We work with ingredient buyers at every stage — from initial specification through to shipment and ongoing supply chain management.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="offer-grid">

        <div class="offer-card">
          <div class="offer-card__num">01</div>
          <h3 class="offer-card__title">Origin Intelligence</h3>
          <p class="offer-card__text">We know which regions grow which botanicals at what quality levels. We know which producers hold which certifications. We know how seasonal variation affects active content and pricing. When you ask us for a specific ingredient, you get a shortlist of vetted producers — not a directory search.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="offer-card">
          <div class="offer-card__num">02</div>
          <h3 class="offer-card__title">Specification Matching</h3>
          <p class="offer-card__text">Whether you need 95% curcuminoids standardised by HPLC, KSM-66 ashwagandha with withanolide certification, or organic moringa at 80 mesh — we match your technical requirements precisely to producer capability. No guesswork. No surprises when the CoA arrives.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="offer-card">
          <div class="offer-card__num">03</div>
          <h3 class="offer-card__title">Certification Navigation</h3>
          <p class="offer-card__text">GMP, ISO 22000, FSSAI, Organic (NPOP/NOP), Halal, Kosher, EU Novel Food compliance, FDA facility registration — we match the right certification stack to every market. Your procurement team shouldn't have to navigate Indian regulatory frameworks. We do it for you.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="offer-card">
          <div class="offer-card__num">04</div>
          <h3 class="offer-card__title">Complete Documentation</h3>
          <p class="offer-card__text">Every ingredient supplied by Ayris Global comes with a full documentation package: Certificate of Analysis, Material Safety Data Sheet, Phytosanitary Certificate, GMP Certificate, and certification documents relevant to your market. Documentation is never an afterthought.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="offer-card">
          <div class="offer-card__num">05</div>
          <h3 class="offer-card__title">Sample Service</h3>
          <p class="offer-card__text">Samples dispatched fast. We understand that your product development timeline doesn't wait for slow supply chains. Sample requests handled with priority — accompanied by full technical data sheets, so your R&D team can evaluate before the sample even arrives.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="offer-card">
          <div class="offer-card__num">06</div>
          <h3 class="offer-card__title">Relationship, Not Transactions</h3>
          <p class="offer-card__text">One point of contact. One team who knows your sourcing programme, understands your market's compliance requirements, and can anticipate what you need before you ask. We build long-term sourcing partnerships — not one-time supplier relationships.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════
       GLOBAL MARKETS
  ════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="markets">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header section-header--light">
        <span class="section-eyebrow section-eyebrow--gold">Where We Work</span>
        <h2 class="section-title section-title--white">Global Markets We Serve</h2>
        <p class="section-sub section-sub--light">Ayris Global partners with buyers across every major wellness market. Our sourcing and documentation capability is calibrated to the specific regulatory environment, cultural preferences, and certification requirements of each region.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="markets-grid">

        <div class="market-card">
          <div class="market-card__region">European Union</div>
          <div class="market-card__divider"></div>
          <p class="market-card__text">EU Regulation 1924/2006 compliant ingredient profiles. Novel Food guidance. EFSA documentation support. Organic EU equivalency via NPOP. Preferred certifications: GMP, ISO 22000, Organic, Halal. High demand for turmeric/curcumin, ashwagandha, moringa, and botanical extracts in DACH, Benelux, Nordics, and Southern Europe.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="market-card">
          <div class="market-card__region">United Kingdom</div>
          <div class="market-card__divider"></div>
          <p class="market-card__text">Post-Brexit UK Food Standards Agency compliance. MHRA-aligned documentation for health claims. Strong functional tea and supplement market — chamomile, tulsi, ashwagandha and adaptogenic blends in high demand from UK health food brands and supermarket own-label formulation teams.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="market-card">
          <div class="market-card__region">United States</div>
          <div class="market-card__divider"></div>
          <p class="market-card__text">FDA facility registration, DSHEA-compliant documentation, cGMP certifications. NOP organic certification for USDA organic label eligibility. The world's largest supplement market — and one where Indian botanical ingredients, particularly ashwagandha, turmeric, and boswellia, hold dominant market positions.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="market-card">
          <div class="market-card__region">UAE / GCC</div>
          <div class="market-card__divider"></div>
          <p class="market-card__text">ESMA and Gulf Standards Organisation compliance. Halal certification mandatory for most ingredients — available across our full range. India's trade relationship with the GCC creates favourable duty structures for qualified exporters. Dubai operates as a re-export hub for broader MENA market access.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="market-card">
          <div class="market-card__region">Japan</div>
          <div class="market-card__divider"></div>
          <p class="market-card__text">MHLW and Food Sanitation Act compliant documentation. Japan's functional food (FOSHU, FFC) and supplement market demands exceptional quality documentation and traceability — areas where Ayris Global's sourcing rigour is directly matched to buyer expectations. Strong demand for cardamom, turmeric, and high-purity botanical extracts.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="market-card">
          <div class="market-card__region">Korea</div>
          <div class="market-card__divider"></div>
          <p class="market-card__text">MFDS and Korea Food Code compliant documentation. Korea's rapidly growing K-wellness and beauty supplement sector has significant appetite for adaptogens, botanical skin actives, and Ayurvedic-derived ingredients. Growing demand for ashwagandha, amla, and neem-derived ingredients in Korean beauty formulations.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="market-card">
          <div class="market-card__region">Australia &amp; New Zealand</div>
          <div class="market-card__divider"></div>
          <p class="market-card__text">TGA (Australia) and Medsafe (NZ) compliant documentation. FSANZ import standards. Organic certification via NPOP-NOP equivalency supports organic label claims in both markets. Strong ANZ market for moringa, turmeric, and herbal wellness formulations — and a growing premium positioning for Indian-origin Ayurvedic ingredients.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="market-card">
          <div class="market-card__region">Southeast Asia</div>
          <div class="market-card__divider"></div>
          <p class="market-card__text">ASEAN member state regulatory compliance across Singapore (HSA), Malaysia (NPRA), Thailand (FDA), Indonesia (BPOM), and Vietnam (DAV). A fast-growing wellness ingredient market with strong cultural affinity for Ayurvedic and traditional botanical ingredients. Halal certification essential across most SEA markets.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="market-card">
          <div class="market-card__region">Latin America</div>
          <div class="market-card__divider"></div>
          <p class="market-card__text">ANVISA (Brazil), INVIMA (Colombia), COFEPRIS (Mexico) and regional MERCOSUR regulatory alignment. LatAm's functional food and supplement sectors are among the world's fastest-growing. Indian botanicals — particularly moringa, turmeric, and ashwagandha — are gaining strong market traction across Brazil, Mexico, and Colombia.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════
       WHO WE WORK WITH
  ════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="buyers">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-eyebrow">Our Buyers</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Who Sources Through Ayris Global</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">We work with a broad range of buyers across the global wellness supply chain — from early-stage brands building their first formulation to established manufacturers expanding their Indian sourcing programme.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="buyers-grid">

        <div class="buyer-type">
          <span class="buyer-type__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="18" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.2"/>
              <path d="M14 20 Q17 13 20 12 Q23 13 26 20 Q23 27 20 28 Q17 27 14 20Z" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.2" fill="none"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <h3>Supplement Brands</h3>
          <p>Brands formulating finished supplements for retail, D2C, and subscription channels. We supply the standardised extracts, powders, and actives that go into your capsules, tablets, and powders — with full documentation for your market.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="buyer-type">
          <span class="buyer-type__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="18" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.2"/>
              <path d="M13 26 L20 12 L27 26" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <path d="M15.5 21 L24.5 21" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <h3>Functional Food &amp; Beverage</h3>
          <p>Food and drink manufacturers adding botanical actives, functional ingredients, and superfoods to their product lines. We supply food-grade botanical powders, extracts, and natural colours with FSANZ, EFSA, and FDA-aligned documentation.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="buyer-type">
          <span class="buyer-type__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="18" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.2"/>
              <circle cx="20" cy="17" r="4" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.2" fill="none"/>
              <path d="M12 30 Q12 24 20 24 Q28 24 28 30" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" fill="none"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <h3>Herbal Tea &amp; Wellness Beverage</h3>
          <p>Tea blenders, herbal infusion brands, and functional beverage producers sourcing culinary-grade dried botanicals — tulsi, hibiscus, chamomile, rose petals, moringa, and spice blends. We supply to specification, with consistent colour, aroma, and microbiological standards.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="buyer-type">
          <span class="buyer-type__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="18" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.2"/>
              <path d="M20 13 L20 20 L26 24" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <path d="M14 16 Q11 20 14 24" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.1" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <path d="M26 16 Q29 20 26 24" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.1" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <h3>Natural Cosmetic &amp; Beauty</h3>
          <p>Skincare, haircare, and beauty supplement brands sourcing botanical actives, essential oils, and plant-derived ingredients. We supply cosmetic-grade botanicals with INCI names, IFRA compliance guidance, and allergen declarations for EU, UK, and global cosmetic regulatory frameworks.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="buyer-type">
          <span class="buyer-type__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="18" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.2"/>
              <rect x="14" y="14" width="12" height="14" rx="1" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.2" fill="none"/>
              <path d="M17 19 L23 19 M17 23 L21 23" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <h3>Private Label &amp; Contract Manufacturers</h3>
          <p>Contract manufacturers and private label producers who need a reliable, audit-ready supply of botanical ingredients to serve their own brand clients. We integrate into your supply chain with the consistency and documentation rigour your clients demand.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="buyer-type">
          <span class="buyer-type__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="18" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.2"/>
              <path d="M13 20 Q14 14 20 13 Q26 14 27 20 Q26 26 20 27 Q14 26 13 20Z" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.2" fill="none"/>
              <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="2.5" fill="#C9A84C"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <h3>Ingredient Distributors</h3>
          <p>Regional ingredient distributors building their Indian botanical portfolio for resale to downstream food, supplement, and cosmetic manufacturers. We supply at distributor volume with the documentation and traceability your customers require.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════
       TRADE ADVANTAGES
  ════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="trade">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="trade__inner">
        <div class="trade__text">
          <span class="section-eyebrow">Sourcing Advantages</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Why Indian Botanicals. Why Now.</h2>
          <p>The global wellness ingredient market is undergoing a structural shift. Buyers who built their supply chains on single-origin European or Chinese botanical sources are diversifying. India has become the preferred alternative — and in many categories, the preferred primary source.</p>
          <p>Here's why buyers across every region are increasing their India sourcing:</p>
        </div>

        <div class="trade__advantages">

          <div class="advantage">
            <div class="advantage__marker" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="advantage__content">
              <h4>Certification Infrastructure at Scale</h4>
              <p>India now has more GMP-certified botanical processing facilities than any other emerging market. Organic, Halal, Kosher, and ISO certifications are available across hundreds of producers — giving buyers access to certified supply at volume.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="advantage">
            <div class="advantage__marker" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="advantage__content">
              <h4>Ingredient Diversity Unmatched Globally</h4>
              <p>From Himalayan herbs to Kerala spices to Rajasthan botanicals — India's climatic and biodiversity range means that an estimated 1,178 medicinal plant species are in active commercial trade, according to National Medicinal Plants Board data, with 242 species traded at volumes exceeding 100 metric tonnes annually. No other single-origin supply chain offers this breadth.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="advantage">
            <div class="advantage__marker" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="advantage__content">
              <h4>Competitive Pricing on Standardised Extracts</h4>
              <p>India's scale in botanical processing means that standardised, HPLC-verified extracts can be sourced at significantly better pricing than equivalent European-processed material — without compromising on quality or certification.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="advantage">
            <div class="advantage__marker" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="advantage__content">
              <h4>Favourable Trade Frameworks</h4>
              <p>India holds preferential trade agreements and frameworks with multiple major markets — including FTAs with the UAE/GCC (CEPA), ASEAN, and ongoing negotiations with the EU and UK. These create duty advantages for qualified exporters that benefit well-structured supply chains.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="advantage">
            <div class="advantage__marker" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="advantage__content">
              <h4>Consumer Demand for Indian Botanicals</h4>
              <p>Ayurveda, adaptogens, and Indian botanical ingredients are not a trend. They are a sustained, decade-long shift in consumer preference across EU, UK, USA, Japan, Korea, and ANZ markets — with brand equity attached to transparent Indian origin.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="advantage">
            <div class="advantage__marker" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="advantage__content">
              <h4>Supply Chain Resilience</h4>
              <p>Post-pandemic procurement strategy across the global wellness industry has prioritised supply chain diversification. India — with its scale, domestic production capacity, and growing export infrastructure — is the natural beneficiary of that shift.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════
       CREDENTIALS
  ════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="credentials">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="credentials__title">Certifications We Source To</h2>
      <p class="credentials__sub">Every market has different certification requirements. We source to match yours.</p>
      <div class="certs-grid">
        <div class="cert-card">
          <span class="cert-card__badge">GMP</span>
          <span class="cert-card__name">Good Manufacturing Practice</span>
          <span class="cert-card__markets">EU · UK · USA · Japan · Korea · ANZ</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cert-card">
          <span class="cert-card__badge">ISO</span>
          <span class="cert-card__name">ISO 22000 / ISO 9001</span>
          <span class="cert-card__markets">All markets</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cert-card">
          <span class="cert-card__badge">FSSAI</span>
          <span class="cert-card__name">Food Safety & Standards Authority of India</span>
          <span class="cert-card__markets">Export compliance</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cert-card">
          <span class="cert-card__badge">Organic</span>
          <span class="cert-card__name">NPOP (India) / NOP (USA)</span>
          <span class="cert-card__markets">EU · UK · USA · ANZ</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cert-card">
          <span class="cert-card__badge">Halal</span>
          <span class="cert-card__name">Halal Certification</span>
          <span class="cert-card__markets">UAE/GCC · SEA · UK · EU</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cert-card">
          <span class="cert-card__badge">Kosher</span>
          <span class="cert-card__name">Kosher Certification</span>
          <span class="cert-card__markets">USA · EU · select markets</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════
       HOW IT WORKS
  ════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="process">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-eyebrow">The Process</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">From Enquiry to Delivered Ingredient</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">A straightforward sourcing process — designed around how ingredient buyers actually work.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="process-steps">

        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="process-step__num">1</div>
          <div class="process-step__content">
            <h3>Submit Your Enquiry</h3>
            <p>Tell us what you need — ingredient, form, specification, certifications required, quantity, and target market. Use our contact form or reach us directly via email or WhatsApp.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="process-step__connector" aria-hidden="true"></div>

        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="process-step__num">2</div>
          <div class="process-step__content">
            <h3>We Match &amp; Confirm</h3>
            <p>Within 48 hours, we confirm availability, matched producer capability, and provide an initial specification sheet and indicative pricing. We'll ask any questions we need to get the match right.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="process-step__connector" aria-hidden="true"></div>

        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="process-step__num">3</div>
          <div class="process-step__content">
            <h3>Sample Dispatch</h3>
            <p>Samples dispatched with full technical documentation — CoA, MSDS, and certification documents relevant to your market. Your R&D team can begin evaluation immediately.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="process-step__connector" aria-hidden="true"></div>

        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="process-step__num">4</div>
          <div class="process-step__content">
            <h3>Order &amp; Shipment</h3>
            <p>On approval, we manage the full order process — producer coordination, quality inspection, export documentation, and shipment. One point of contact throughout.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════
       CTA
  ════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="cta-band">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-band__inner">
        <h2 class="cta-band__title">Ready to start a sourcing conversation?</h2>
        <p class="cta-band__sub">Whether you have a precise specification or you're still exploring which ingredients work for your formulation — we're happy to help. Start with an enquiry and we'll take it from there.</p>
        <div class="cta-band__actions">
          <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg">Submit a Sourcing Enquiry</a>
          <a href="/products/" class="btn btn--ghost btn--lg">Explore Ingredient Categories</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ─────────────────────────────
     PAGE HERO
  ───────────────────────────── */
  .page-hero {
    background: #1B2B4B;
    padding: 7rem 1.5rem 5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-hero__inner {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.75);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .page-hero__title {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif;
